804
00:50:18,087 --> 00:50:21,376
I get a call on the day of the surgery as if it's a picnic.

805
00:50:21,527 --> 00:50:22,606
How...

806
00:50:26,596 --> 00:50:28,577
You shouldn't do that to your daughter.

807
00:50:29,697 --> 00:50:31,646
