873
00:55:27,266 --> 00:55:28,376
Okay.

874
00:55:32,596 --> 00:55:35,067
Ha Ri, I need to get a film...

875
00:55:35,067 --> 00:55:37,277
for the camera.

876
00:55:37,277 --> 00:55:38,387
